
The makerepos.pl is written in perl and depends on the perl module Config::Properties.

To install that it is best to use CPAN.
Recipe:
steps: 
1 start CPAN and update and reload it. (first three lines)
2 install Config::Properties (cpan> is the prompt. Do not type)
cut -----

perl -MCPAN -e shell
cpan> install Bundle::CPAN
cpan> reload cpan
cpan> install Config::Properties

cut ---

